DATABASE_URL=Postgres connection string used by the Drizzle/Neon database layer.
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=Random secret used by NextAuth for session encryption.
JWT_SECRET=Secret used to sign the custom JWT cookies for email/password auth.
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=Google OAuth client ID for the NextAuth Google provider.
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=Google OAuth client secret for the NextAuth Google provider.
